						               													<description>This is a ONE CARD version of Movie Plotz, conveniently printed on plastic so that you can put it in your wallet! It's the size of a credit card and offers the Movie Plotz experience in an even smaller footprint.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;&amp;mdash;description from the publisher&amp;#10;&amp;#10;&amp;#10;Movie Plotz is a wild game that allows your group to create hilarious fake movie storylines, then pitch them out loud for maximum laughs. Movie Plotz was designed as a very effective team building event that has evolved into a crazy party game where everyone contributes to the fun.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;Players begin with a simple plot (a simple sentence) then choose a challenge/modifier from a list (instead of a card) to modify the movie concept. With each change, players get to redo the pitch and make it even more exciting. In the end, the final plot will be a guaranteed hit!&amp;#10;&amp;#10;Depending on the rules variation that you choose to play, the player with the most points will win.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;</description>
